Rando is a simple picture-sharing app
It is built using the Dwyco messaging system back-end.

Current requirements:
* Qt 6.8+

Note: this is really intended as mobile phone app, but it builds
ok for desktop as well. This makes it easier to debug.

May 2019
Deployed to google play store

(WARNING: Tue Mar  3 11:55:32 AM MST 2026, moving frm ndk-build to cmake for android builds, so things may not build right for awhile)
